707967f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Avenue - 120th Street
707967f-a.text:
Second avenue, west side, from 120th to 121st Streets,showing
2341-2345 Second avenue, two two-story frame houses at and
adjoining the N. W. corner of 120th Street.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection,Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 260,

707966f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Avenue - 120th Street
707966f-a.text:
Second Avenue at N. W. corner of 120th Street, showing 2341-2345
Second Avenue, the corner buildings, two frame houses which
will still stand in 1934.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection,Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 150,
